16ebb4f443b74f\",\n    \"ref\": \"refs/heads/main\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-08T03:47:03Z\",\n    \"activity_type\": \"pr_merge\",\n    \"actor\": {","cwd":"/home/node/.openclaw/workspace/researcher"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772942638406}}
